title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When exporting data in two tables, an exception is thrown in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' method.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the data should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert one table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
